Kelly Reilly https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kelly_Reilly 0 Jessica Kelly Siobhán Reilly (born 18 July 1977), better known by the stage name Kelly Reilly, is an Anglo-Irish actress. Her performance in After Miss Julie at the Donmar Warehouse made her a star of the London stage and earned her a nomination for a Laurence Olivier Award for Best Actress of 2003. Débuting 20 June 2018, Reilly is the female lead in the new American Paramount Network's cowboy-themed drama series, Yellowstone.
